    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694880/extras/c54e2a6328bef4ab6051a557901cb58f.poster.avif?t=1728497379\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694880/extras/c54e2a6328bef4ab6051a557901cb58f.webm?t=1728497379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694880/extras/c54e2a6328bef4ab6051a557901cb58f.mp4?t=1728497379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Spectrolite</strong>是一款发生在第一视角下的趣味游戏，您可以在其中体验到刺激的氛围和紧张的限时挑战相结合的乐趣。我们在传统跑酷形式上进一步优化，从而提高了操作的精确度。<br>在我们的游戏中，您可以享受到各种不同的场景和音乐，以及简短的计时赛。您还可以与来自全球的玩家一同切磋技艺，并且通过观察别的玩家的“幽灵”来掌握每个跑酷技能。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694880/extras/b9a9991680c235dda73e6b83ec20ceb0.poster.avif?t=1728497379\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694880/extras/b9a9991680c235dda73e6b83ec20ceb0.webm?t=1728497379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694880/extras/b9a9991680c235dda73e6b83ec20ceb0.mp4?t=1728497379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特征</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 探索大规模的、独立制作的关卡<br></li><li> 多种原创背景音乐<br></li><li> 精确的控制<br></li><li> 在计时赛中提升个人记录<br></li><li> 在全球排行榜上竞争</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694880/extras/eda9cddce1eab1c91798c12c5cc6648e.poster.avif?t=1728497379\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694880/extras/eda9cddce1eab1c